  "detailed_description": "Knight Runner: Blade and Bolt is a simple, top-down, endless runner where you must fight your way through a monster-infested forest, dodging traps, collecting powerups, and timing your strikes to compete for a spot on the global leaderboard.<br><br>There is no meta-progression here — the only goal is to make it as far through the forest as you can!<br><br>Chain kills to trigger the multiplier and reach new high scores. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942430/extras/ae5f4750ee42f41bdae74e468f76df18.poster.avif?t=1716240297\" width=506 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942430/extras/ae5f4750ee42f41bdae74e468f76df18.webm?t=1716240297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Play with keyboard and mouse, or a controller. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942430/extras/d61bf217582f8444726d979765bcfa6e.avif?t=1716240297\" width=640 height=240 /></span><br><br>Collect upgrades and powerups from chests while fighting thirteen types of monsters.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942430/extras/02d33caebc3d7c90575d900d29c0b3bb.poster.avif?t=1716240297\" width=506 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942430/extras/02d33caebc3d7c90575d900d29c0b3bb.webm?t=1716240297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Knight Runner: Blade and Bolt is a simple, top-down, endless runner where you must fight your way through a monster-infested forest, dodging traps, collecting powerups, and timing your strikes to compete for a spot on the global leaderboard.<br><br>There is no meta-progression here — the only goal is to make it as far through the forest as you can!<br><br>Chain kills to trigger the multiplier and reach new high scores. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942430/extras/ae5f4750ee42f41bdae74e468f76df18.poster.avif?t=1716240297\" width=506 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942430/extras/ae5f4750ee42f41bdae74e468f76df18.webm?t=1716240297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Play with keyboard and mouse, or a controller. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942430/extras/d61bf217582f8444726d979765bcfa6e.avif?t=1716240297\" width=640 height=240 /></span><br><br>Collect upgrades and powerups from chests while fighting thirteen types of monsters.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942430/extras/02d33caebc3d7c90575d900d29c0b3bb.poster.avif?t=1716240297\" width=506 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942430/extras/02d33caebc3d7c90575d900d29c0b3bb.webm?t=1716240297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
